a panel, right?

01:06:13.709 --> 01:06:14.709
The panel is a comedy show, I'm a straight
man economist.

01:06:14.709 --> 01:06:15.709
And they said, "Why are you presenting a panel?"
And I says, "Because I do stuff."

01:06:15.709 --> 01:06:16.709
And that's what I do in life.
