01:06:23.709 --> 01:06:24.709
it from a macro-economic view, and costs are
falling -- some people say it's a good thing.

01:06:24.709 --> 01:06:25.709
But I don't think the environment for us has
changed at all.

01:06:25.709 --> 01:06:26.709
We just do stuff in different environments.
So if like, for example, the way I look at

01:06:26.709 --> 01:06:27.709
it is, people say, "Do the panel?"
I say, "Yeah, do it." And enjoy it.

01:06:27.709 --> 01:06:28.709
So I don't think -- I think what happens in
Ireland is this extraordinary thing that -- we

01:06:28.709 --> 01:06:29.709
have to fix the big things.
But if we wait until we fix the big -- it's

01:06:29.709 --> 01:06:30.709
like in Google.
I mean, I presume you don't wait around for

01:06:30.709 --> 01:06:31.709
direction from on high to do stuff.
And this is what I think -- the sort of environment

01:06:31.709 --> 01:06:32.709
that you've created here -- if we could replicate
that outside.

01:06:32.709 --> 01:06:33.709
